<rss version="2.0"><channel><title>经济学家</title><description>经济学人全文RSS。获取更多全文RSS：https://feedx.net</description><link/> https://www.economist.com <item><title><![CDATA[Mark Zuckerberg’s smart move was a brief pause from the metaverse | Podcasts]]></title><link/><![CDATA[https://www.economist.com/podcasts/2023/11/28/mark-zuckerbergs-smart-move-was-a-brief-pause-from-the-metaverse]]><description> &lt;img src=&quot;https://images.weserv.nl/?url=www.economist.com/img/b/1280/720/90/media-assets/image/20231202_PDP503.jpg&quot;/>;&lt;div>;&lt; /div>;&lt;p data-caps=&quot;initial&quot;>;&lt;span data-caps=&quot;initial&quot;>;T&lt;/span>;&lt;small>;他单一&lt;/small>;专注于 Meta 老板 Mark Zuckerberg 的虚拟世界，令投资者焦躁不安。但在过去的一年里，他取得了惊人的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.economist.com/business/2023/10/26/ai-has-rescued-mark-zuckerberg-from-a-metaverse- size-hole&quot; data-tegid=&quot;vfcp2t36egt5hu5f7ql45m5knfadu0c1&quot;>;及时周转&lt;/a>;。我们看看是什么推动了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.economist.com/the-americas/2023/11/09/illegal-gold-is-booming-in-south-america&quot; data-tegid= “i8l41uuch8rhs0p85s8ai6rvn03acccb&quot;>;委内瑞拉的非法淘金热&lt;/a>;作为更广泛的区域问题的镜头 (9:48)。以及为什么朝鲜女子足球队提供这样的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.economist.com/culture/2023/10/26/north-koreas-secret-sporting-weapon&quot; data-tegid=&quot;dduhec1ea33i9iplg1abap6hbr24kjjd&quot;>;良好的宣传&lt;/a>; (16:48)。运行时间：22 分钟&lt;/p>;&lt;div>;&lt;figure>;&lt;div>;&lt;figcaption>;收听此播客&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/div>;&lt;audiocontrols=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;audio-player&quot; preload=&quot;none&quot; src=&quot;https://sphinx.acast.com/p/acast/s/theintelligencepodcast/e/6565bf838eb9a90011a23490/media.mp3?tk=eyJ1aWQiOiJ0b20iLCJ0ayI6ImZHeExMd3dDIiwiYWRzIjpmYWxzZSwic3BvbnMiOmZhbH NlLCJzdGF0dXMiOiJwdWJsaWMifQ==&amp;sig=dPiYWdo8USuXYoYStwEEpQiYv-giv5MtR4_JZiowa8M&quot; title=&quot;情报&quot;controlsList= &quot;nodownload&quot;>;&lt;p>;您的浏览器不支持&lt;音频>;元素。&lt;/p>;&lt;/audio>;&lt;div>;&lt;div>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/figure>;&lt;/div>;&lt;p>;&lt;i>;注册&lt;a href=&quot;https:// /www.eco